    conditioning: ['Agility Ladder Quick Feet: Run through the agility ladder with rapid in-out foot patterns, 4 sets of 3 ladder lengths with 30-second rest between sets for foot speed.', 'Fast Singles Jump Rope: Jump rope at maximum speed with single bounces for 3 rounds of 3 minutes — builds the calf endurance and foot speed that directly transfers to sustained shuffle-stepping.', 'Mirror Partner Drill: Face a partner and match their movements exactly through shuffle steps for 3 rounds of 2 minutes — the follower practices reactive shuffling while the leader practices deceptive rhythm changes.'],
